Veenendaal.title: Veenendaal
Veenendaal.byline: Veenendaal is a town in Utrecht, with around 63000 inhabitants.

Veenkoloniën.title: Veenkoloniën
Veenkoloniën.byline: The (Groninger) Veenkoloniën (Dutch for Peat Colonies (of Groningen city)) or Peat District is a region in the southeast of the province of Groningen, the Netherlands.
